body.name: HMCYCI LED Bulbs Combo Fit For DODGE RAM 1500 2500 3500 4-Headlamps (2009-2018),9005+H11 High/Low Beam + 9145/9140 Fog Light Bulbs,Super Bright Cool White, Plug and Play, Pack of 6
features: 💖- If you have a Dodge Ram 1500 2500 3500 (2009-2018) and are looking to upgrade your Headlights, our Headlight Bulbs are the perfect solution. These bulbs are designed specifically for the Dodge Ram 1500 2500 3500 (2013-2018) models, making installation a breeze. This pack of 6 includes for both high and low beams LED Bulbs, as well as fog lights Bulbs to give your truck a cleaner and more modern look.

💖- Super Bright 6500K Cool White: The bulbs are 400% brighter than original halogen bulbs, mimicking the original halogen beam pattern but with a brighter, more focused beam. The 6500K cool white color temperature creates a crisper and clearer beam that enhances visibility on the road.

💖- Plug and Play: The bulbs have a 1:1 size ratio with halogens, making them easy to install without the need for any tools. With the perfect fit, you can install them in just a few minutes, and the built-in driver ensures complete compatibility with most vehicle computer systems without any error codes or flickering.

💖- IP68ratedwateranddustseal: These bulbs are waterproof and dustproof, with an IP68 rating that ensures they can withstand all weather conditions. You can safely use them in rainy, dusty, or foggy conditions without worrying about damage to the bulbs or reduced performance.

💖 This product is a combination of high beam and low beam and Fog light ,Built-in constant current CPU, instant full brightness without start-up relay. ,It is important to note that these bulbs are 98% compatible with most vehicles. We strongly recommend referring to the owner's manual or original bulb's part number before purchasing this product.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Brand :HMCYCI HMCYCI is a brand that specializes in LED lighting solutions for automobiles. Our team has years of experience in providing innovative and high-quality products to automotive enthusiasts worldwide. We strive to create products that not only look great but also provide incredible performance.

ENJOY YOUR DRIVING WITH HMCYCI SERIES LED HEADLIGHT KIT ALL IN ONE COMPACT DESIGN Great Brightness - 120W, 20000LM per pair, 1800FT visibility. 400% brighter than your original halogen lamps. Perfect Beam Pattern - Super focused beam pattern, no dark spots or foggy light, do not blind oncoming traffic. Plug and Play - Almost 1:1 mini design as halogen, easy and quick to install in 10 minutes without any modification. CanBUS Ready - Work with 99% of vehicles without computer system error problems. Adjustable Beam - Adopts 360° adjustable locker ring to ensure the best beam pattern. Efficient Cooling System - Whole aviation aluminum body, unique hollow-carved heat sink and 12,000 RPM turbofan provide excellent cooling ability to ensure 50,000 hours No fear of extremely weather. IP68 waterproof level makes the LED headlights performed well in any poor conditions. Super durability in rainy day, foggy day, snowy day,etc.

Product Function Detailed Explanation: Our LED headlights feature top-grade 3570 LED chips that offer super bright 6500K cool white light with a focused beam pattern design. With 120W and 20000LM per pair, which is 400% brighter than original halogen bulbs, they provide wider and farther lighting range that makes signs, reflectors, and lane markings highly visible on rural roads and in mountainous areas. The high/low beam headlights perfectly mimic the original halogen beam pattern, and the fog lights enhance visibility in adverse weather conditions. Specification Information and Usage Instructions: - Light Source Model: Super Bright 3570 Chip - Power: 60W/bulb - Lumen: 10000LM/bulb - Operating Voltage: DC9-36V - Material: 6063 Aviation Aluminum - Beam Angle: 360 degrees - Color Temperature: 6500K Cool White - Lifespan: over 50000 hours

Frequently Asked Questions: Q: What if it flicker or come out an error after installation? A: Decoders may be required for few extremely sensitive vehicle. Since LED conversion kits use less power than halogen or HID bulbs, it can be a problem if your vehicle comes with a CANBUS system, as it may think your lights are fault and causing them to work improperly. You can find them on online or let us know. Q: Why one of headlights cannot work well? A: The decoder may be solved this issue. The decoder issue appears flicker on&off/on board error/only one side works, etc. Especially the bulbs cannot work on the driver side. Q: Why both of them don't work after installation? A: Please check the polarity when connecting the plug. You can plug the headlights into the connector in any way, but the wrong polarity will cause the led bulbs to not work properly. Please try to turn the plug over and reconnect it. Q: Why the headlight don't fit my vehicle even though website said it would. A: The filter system may not be 100% accurate or up to date, if you are not sure about the type, please confirm with us before purchasing.
